badges.description:
oooo Explorer Badge is awarded for users who have made 3 bridge transactions to scroll on oooo bridge: https://bridge.oooo.money/?token=ETH&from=bsc&to=scroll.

Reward Explanation:

1. Users can earn 8 Goooo & 80 Lumoz Points of each transaction. Claim at https://bridge.oooo.money/goooo;
2. Users can receive an O-Voucher Pack containing 20 O-Vouchers, which deduct up to 50% of bridge fees for any token, after completing their first transaction. Claim at: https://bridge.oooo.money/o-voucher;
3. Users can get an exclusive Explorer Badge after completing 3 transactions.
